snippet.title: Starcraft 2 | Resurgence of the Storm | Closed Playtesting Gameplay #32
snippet.description:
Resurgence of the Storm is a Starcraft 2 arcade map that is currently being developed by zeroLamberg inside the Starcraft 2 Galaxy Editor.

You can come follow the progress at https://discord.gg/QjdgCQPWtA
